මධ්‍යම අධිවේගී මාර්ගය  පිවිසුම් 5-6 ක් කුරුණෑගල දිස්ත්‍රික්කයේ දැනටමත් සංවර්ධනය වෙමින් පවතී.   1. නාකලගමුව පිවිසුම- නාරම්මල ප්‍රදේශයට පැමිණේ. (මීගමු-කුරුණෑගල මාර්ගයට එක් වෙන ලෙස)  2. පොතුහැර පිවිසුම - පොතුහැර ප්‍රදේශයට පැමිණේ. (කොළඹ -කුරුණෑගල මාර්ගයට එක් වෙන ලෙස). මෙම පිවිසුමෙන් මහනුවර අධිවේගී මාර්ගය ඉදිවේ.  3. දම්බොක්ක පිවිසුම- දම්බොක්ක ප්‍රදේශයට පැමිණේ. (කොළඹ-කුරුණෑගල මාර්ගයට එක් වෙන ලෙස)  4. කුරුණෑගල ප්‍රධාන පිවිසුම- තෙලියගොන්න ප්‍රදේශයට පැමිණේ. (කුරුණෑගල- නුවර මාර්ගයට එක් වෙන ලෙස)  5. මැල්සිරිපුර පිවිසුම - මැල්සිරිපුර ප්‍රදේශයට පැමිණේ. (කුරුණෑගල- දඹුල්ල මාර්ගයට එක් වෙන ලෙස)  6. රිදීගම පිවිසුම - රිදීගම ප්‍රදේශයට පැමිණේ. . . . #highway #CentralExpressway #kurunegala #kurunegalalandsale #kurunegalarealestate #property #kurunegalaproperty #cbhlands #puttlam #colombo #dambulla #kandy #colombo #realestate #property #landsale

මධ්‍යම අධිවේගී මාර්ගය  පිවිසුම් 5-6 ක් කුරුණෑගල දිස්ත්‍රික්කයේ දැනටමත් සංවර්ධනය වෙමින් පවතී.   1. නාකලගමුව පිවිසුම- නාරම්මල ප්‍රදේශයට පැමිණේ. (මීගමු-කුරුණෑගල මාර්ගයට එක් වෙන ලෙස)  2. පොතුහැර පිවිසුම - පොතුහැර ප්‍රදේශයට පැමිණේ. (කොළඹ -කුරුණෑගල මාර්ගයට එක් වෙන ලෙස). මෙම පිවිසුමෙන් මහනුවර අධිවේගී මාර්ගය ඉදිවේ.  3. දම්බොක්ක පිවිසුම- දම්බොක්ක ප්‍රදේශයට පැමිණේ. (කොළඹ-කුරුණෑගල මාර්ගයට එක් වෙන ලෙස)  4. කුරුණෑගල ප්‍රධාන පිවිසුම- තෙලියගොන්න ප්‍රදේශයට පැමිණේ. (කුරුණෑගල- නුවර මාර්ගයට එක් වෙන ලෙස)  5. මැල්සිරිපුර පිවිසුම - මැල්සිරිපුර ප්‍රදේශයට පැමිණේ. (කුරුණෑගල- දඹුල්ල මාර්ගයට එක් වෙන ලෙස)  6. රිදීගම පිවිසුම - රිදීගම ප්‍රදේශයට පැමිණේ. . . . #investinland #kurunegala #kurunegalarealestate #kurunegalalands #kurunegalaproperty #buyland #invest #investment #investing #investinland #money #wealth #srilanka #howto #mortgage #bankloan #finance #realestate #realestateinvestment #cbhlands #centralexpresswat #highwaynetwork #highway #narammala #dambokka #pothuhera #melsiripura #ridigama #rideegama

For thousands of years, Real Estate has been one of the most popular investments; around the world. Bare land, in particular, is bought mostly as a long term, very low risk investment.   In the reason past, Millenials, those who are born between 1981- 1996, have gone back to buying more bare lands, than the previous generation. Why?  Millenials, unlike other generations, may not purchase property to live; but they buy as an investment. And also, they buy property looking at the "potential growth"! Which means, unlike Generation X, who are more interested in current situation (ex: if the area is developed now), Millenials look at what it could be in the future.  This is why we never underestimate the younger generations' decision making! . . . #millenials #young #generation #generationx #babyboomers #buyingbehaviour #cbhlands #realestateinvestment #mondaymotivation #monday #research #realestate #kurunegala #srilanka #currentvalue #futurevalue #decisionmaking #generationgap #land #landsale #histroy #fact #bareland #longterm #investment #rich #money #wealth

(කුරුණෑගල- දඹුල්ල මාර්ගයට එක් වෙන ලෙස) 6. රිදීගම පිවිසුම - රිදීගම ප්‍රදේශයට පැමිණේ.  මධ්‍යම අධිවේගී මාර්ග පිවිසුම් අසළ, ඉඩම් සහ දේපළවලට ඇති ඉල්ලුම දැනටමත් වැඩි වෙමින් පවතියි.   ඔබ තවමත් ප්‍රමාද නැත. ගෙවීමේ ක්‍රමයකින්, මෙවැනි, ඉඩමකට ආයෝජනය කරන්න. කුරුණෑගල දිස්ත්‍රික්කයට අධිවේගී මාර්ග පිවිසුම් 6 තැනෙනවා. මෙම පිවිසුම්වලට ලඟින් ඉඩමකට ආයෝජනය කරන්න.  වැඩි විස්තර සඳහා Message/ Call කරන්න.   . . . . . #cbhlands #landsale #kurunegala #kurunegalarealestate #kurunegalaproperty #landforsale #highway #srilankahighways #kurunegalahighway #centralexpressway #dambokka #dambokkainterchange #landsnearhighway #buyland #invest #invetsment #land #realestate #property #easy #wealth #money #rich #buy #sale #discount #bank #invest #land #license #property  #developer #kurunegalaland #investinland #mortgage #bankloan  #income #savings  #interest #home #build #kurunegalarproperty

In this prevailing low interest rate environment, funds held in banks provide negative returns, as they offer only 5 percent per annum, while the actual inflation is above 11 percent. Thus, one receives a negative return of about 7 percent minimum per annum by holding funds in the bank. Therefore, it is very important that you invest cleverly and real estate, if selected carefully, offers the best returns. Violence a Destruction  He was sitting on the grass with a tea in his left hand speaking to her at the protest site. He looked at the sunrise, and she at the tea in her hand. They spoke about the peaceful protest that had been held for the 31st day straight. Their intentions were peaceful, as many millions of protestors had attended with their families over the past weeks. It was their 21st day straight at the protest site. Proud of themselves and the progress made. They knew it was never going to be easy.   Their intentions and actions have been continuously peaceful. The activities at the protest site have not only been peaceful, but very innovative and colorful.  A colorful revolution. She said that their generation was on the verge of transforming the entire country. They had achieved unimaginable progress towards transforming their future. Not only their future but the future of the past, present and future generations. He said the peaceful protest was unprecedented. They spoke about Ghandi, Martin Luther King and even Nelsen Mandela. They expected a positive outcome that day. This was a massive victory. A victory achieved through non-violence. A great achievement for innocent people.   Now she sits at the same location in the dark physically beaten by mobs. Whilst he is at hospital assaulted. She thinks of him. She does not know how well he is doing. Whether he is ok? Whether he is thinking of her? Whether he knows she is ok? She wants quick news. But there is no communication. Her tears continue to fall. Tears of sorrow mixed with courage to continue the fight through non – violent means stronger than before. She knows that they will win. She knows her courage is far greater than the goons and thugs.   The cronies and thugs used violence in an unprecedented manner. They took the law to their hands. Abused the innocent non-violent protestors. Although, they were brutally assaulted; determination, righteousness, humility, patience, long suffering and non-violence has been the cornerstone of their struggle for a future that can be rejoiced and celebrated.   Today, she thought that we are marching towards our goal. Success will come their way. The peaceful struggle will continue.   She looked to the dark sky. She received a message from him. “hope you will get this message, How are you? I am ok” he wrote.     We at CBH Land condemn the use of violence in this non-violent, peaceful and humble movement on innocent protestors.
